<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cookie Bliss</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Cookie Bliss</h1>
            <p>Your daily dose of sweetness, one cookie at a time.</p>
            <a href="#order" class="cta-button">Order Now</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
                At Cookie Bliss, we bake every cookie with love, using the finest ingredients to bring joy to your taste buds. 
                Whether you’re craving classic chocolate chip or adventurous new flavors, we’ve got you covered.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="flavors">
            <h2>Our Best-Selling Flavors</h2>
            <div class="flavor-grid">
                <div class="flavor-card">
                    <img src="/images/chocolate-chip.jpg" alt="Chocolate Chip Cookie">
                    <h3>Chocolate Chip</h3>
                    <p>The timeless classic, baked to perfection.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flavor-card">
                    <img src="/images/red-velvet.jpg" alt="Red Velvet Cookie">
                    <h3>Red Velvet</h3>
                    <p>Soft, velvety, and irresistible.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flavor-card">
                    <img src="/images/peanut-butter.jpg" alt="Peanut Butter Cookie">
                    <h3>Peanut Butter</h3>
                    <p>Rich and nutty for peanut lovers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="order" id="order">
            <h2>Order Your Cookies</h2>
            <p>Call us at <strong>555-COOKIE</strong> or visit us at <a href="https://www.cookiebliss.com">www.cookiebliss.com</a></p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Cookie Bliss. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
